      <title>ivelchampion249/FishSol-Macro</title>
      <link>https://github.com/ivelchampion249/FishSol-Macro</link>
      <description>Works on 1920x1080, 2560x1440, and 1366x768. Must be on 100% zoom and Fullscreen. Firstly, you want to walk over to the Fisherman NPC (Captain Flarg), and open the sell menu and keep it open. After that, walk over to your favorite fishing spot. Press F1 to activate the macro, F2 to pause the macro, and F3 to force close.</description>
